headline: How the Investment Story for State Street Is Shifting Amid Analyst Upgrades and Market Developments
summary: State Street’s stock narrative is evolving as the consensus analyst price target has risen slightly, moving from $127.30 to $129.63 per share. This change comes amidst a cautiously optimistic outlook from Wall Street. Analysts are pointing to strong revenue performance and improving fee growth.
